  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed replacement summerhouse, by reason of its size, detailed design, and materials, is an incongruous and uncharacteristic form of development that fails to be subservient enough to the host building and fails to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of the De Beauvoir Conservation Area. As such the proposal is contrary to policies HC1 (Heritage, Conservation, and Growth) and D3 (Optimising Site Capacity through the Design-led Approach) of the London Plan (2021) and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character), and LP3 (Designated Heritage Assets) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020) and Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/p&gt;"
